TI  - Leveraging Cloud-Fog Automation for Autonomous Collision Detection and Classification in Intelligent Unmanned Surface Vehicles
PY  - 2025
T2  - IEEE International Conference on Industrial Informatics (INDIN)
DO  - 10.1109/INDIN64977.2025.11279683
