TI  - Challenges in the Supply Chain Management Process for Offshore Wind Farms. A Scoping Review of Decision Support Tools Utilizing Discrete Event Simulation
PY  - 2026
T2  - TransNav
VL  - 20
IS  - 1
SP  - 187
