TI  - BRIDGING THE GAP: ORGANISATIONAL PERCEPTIONS AND ADOPTION STRATEGIES FOR DIGITAL TWINS AND GEOLOGICAL HYDROGEN STORAGE IN THE ENERGY TRANSITION
PY  - 2025
