AB  - The evaluation of the reliability of the energy Internet cyber-physical system is complicated, and the mechanism of interaction and mutual influence between the energy primary equipment level and the information terminal level is still difficult to be clarified. In this paper, we establish the node potential function and network topology potential function for measuring the energy Internet information support based on the data field theory and propose the node importance evaluation index system and the generalized node quality calculation method with evaluation offset optimization to realize the objective evaluation of the reliability of the energy Internet cyber-physical system. © 2023 SPIE.
