TI  - Fullest COLREGs Evaluation Using Fuzzy Logic for Collaborative Decision-Making Analysis of Autonomous Ships in Complex Situations
PY  - 2022
T2  - IEEE Transactions on Intelligent Transportation Systems
VL  - 23
IS  - 10
