AB  - This system adopts the technology of digital earth and UE engine, which separates the digital twin technology base from the secondary development and deduction rules of specific scenarios, in order to achieve fast and convenient design of specific disaster scenarios, user-defined deduction and evaluation rules. For the simultaneous online interactive drilling of various posts at the port, the system can present real-time simulation results in three-dimensional form, statistically display relevant information of damage and response effect, and evaluate the cooperative and coordinated mechanism of various posts in the disaster plan. This system can discuss and evaluate the coordinated emergency plans of various departments more truthfully, scientifically, and reliably, which helps to provide immersive emergency training for the personnel of various positions in the port, and has reference value for departmental coordinated disaster emergency deduction in other regions. © 2024 SPIE.
