AB  - AI in the Navy? Dreams of the future or state-of-the-art? Here, two approaches for the use of ML procedures on ships are presented and possible prerequisites for creating awareness for them. Condition monitoring using the example of power generation and the identification of other naval vessels serve to illustrate ML-based cyber-physical systems and their benefits. With their good results, both methods testify to the advantages for the Navy to increasingly deal with the use of AI on board in the future.  © 2022 The Authors. Published by Elsevier B.V.
