AB  - The present paper proposes a technical path to build a smart port through digital twin. Focusing on the port production business, this paper analyzes the demand of the combination of business management and technology application, and puts forward the overall construction framework. On this basis, two scenarios of dry bulk cargo loading and unloading operation and container yard operation are implemented by digital twin software, which verifies the rationality of the overall framework. The port digital twin software developed has played a positive role in improving the production efficiency, reducing the operation risk of on-site personnel, controlling personnel costs, and improving the scientific decision-making. © ISPM 2021.All right reserved.
