AB  - This study is a study to build a virtual crane simulation system for technical research related to remote monitoring and preventive maintenance of marine crane system. In this study, we have studied the construction method of crane system for virtual simulation system. Remote monitoring of the crane system and construction of the actual system for the development of the preventive maintenance technology is necessary, but this system can be an alternative when the crane system can't be built or the system can't be built. The simulation system developed in this study has kinematic and kinematic modelling for CPS based simulation. In order to achieve the near realistic effect of each component according to the operation of the system by developing the closest to the actual crane system. These studies are expected to contribute to the research and application of digital twin systems in the marine sector. © 2019, Avestia Publishing.
