TI  - Exploring the effects of technology and innovation on changing market requirements and the evolving maritime curriculum: A Jamaican perspective
PY  - 2020
T2  - Worldwide Hospitality and Tourism Themes
VL  - 12
IS  - 1
SP  - 69
EP  - 79
